---
layout: layouts/base
---

<main>
  <h1 class="text-2xl mt-8">Hi, I'm Brian.</h1>
  <p class="mb-0">
    I'm a software engineer at <a href="https://askflux.ai">askflux.ai</a>.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-0">
    I've been doing full stack dev for about 12 years, mostly in Django.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-0">I read and write about theology and tech.</p>
  <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8">Recent Notes</h2>
  <p class="italic text-xs">
    Small notes on technical things, written as I work. Lightly edited, if at
    allâ€”caveat lector.
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
    {%- for post in collections.note reversed -%}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">
        {{ post.data.title }}
        <time datetime="{{ post.data.page.date | date : '%Y-%m-%d' }}">
          [ {{ post.data.page.date | date : "%B %d, %Y" }} ]
        </time>
      </a>
    </li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
  <h2 class="text-2xl mt-8">Recent Links</h2>
  <p class="italic text-xs">Interesting things from around the web.</p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
    {%- for post in collections.link reversed -%}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">
        <span class="italic">{{ post.data.title }}.</span>
        <span>{{ post.data.author }}.</span>
        <time datetime="{{ post.data.page.date | date : '%Y-%m-%d' }}">
          {{ post.data.page.date | date : "%B %d, %Y" }}.
        </time>
      </a>
    </li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
</main>
